AKAPHELI moya umfundisi Alph Lukau obe sematheni nonyaka kulandela ukusabalala kwevideo yakhe ‘evusa’ umuntu ekufeni. Lo mfundisi webandla i-Alleluia Ministries uphenduke inhlekisa kuleli ngemuva kokusabalala kwale video ezinkundleni zokuxhumana okwacacela iningi ukuthi kuyalingiswa kuyo. Ngemuva kokuhamba kwesikhathi lo mfundisi washaya ungqimphothwe wathi empeleni owesilisa (Elliot Moyo) abonakala emuvusa kwivideo wafika evele esephila kuye. Ngenyanga edlule kuboshwe ababili ngalesi simangaliso kulandela ukuvulelwa kwebandla likaLukau icala lokudicilela isithunzi sezinkampani ezintathu zokungcwaba ezasentshinziswa kwakhiwa isimangaliso. ULukau ugxekwe kakhulu ngalesi ‘simangaliso’ kangangokuba omunye umfundisi obegxekwa abanye abaholi bezenkolo ngezintshumayelo zakhe, uPastor Paseka ‘Mboro’ Motsoeneng, naye wangenelela wathi wehlise isithunzi sabefundisi. Ngaphezu kwalokho uhlelo oluphenya ngezihloko ezihlukene kuleli olukhonjiswa kwiSABC iCutting Edge, lwakhuluma namanye amalungu ebandla lakhe adalula ukuthi ayekhokhelwa imali ukuze alingise azenze abantu abagulayo. Konke lokhu nokho akubukeki kuphazamisa umsebenzi kaLukau kulempelesonto ophinde wafaka izithombe enza izimangaliso ebandleni lakhe. Kulokhu ubonakala evusa abantu ‘asebegulela ukufa’.